item.title: Participants registration For Malaysia Open Source Conference MOSC MY 2017 is now open
item.description: Participants registration For Malaysia Open Source Conference MOSC MY 2017 is now open. Please visit the link below for registration fee and ticket. We are using Eventbrite and Paypal as payment gateway. Participants registration : https://moscmy2017.eventbrite.com or http://moscmalaysia.eventbrite.com/ Registration by Local Order (government) or payment by cheque, or you could not used PayPal payment gateway. Offilne payment available. Register yourself by click “Get Tickets” and select you ticket type and Checkout.

item.title: Target Audience MOSC MY 2016
item.description: Technical managers, administrators, developers and expert users from the following organisations: Government : All ministries and agencies Academics : All public and private universities and colleges Business : All MNC, Public Listed Companies, Technology Venture Capital Companies, Telecommunication, Banking, Transportation and Services Industries. Community : All OSS communities that have representation in Malaysia Target Audience MOSC My 2016
